The paper discusses the results and evaluation of the RoboCup 2D Soccer Simulation League, which involves artificial intelligence and robotics (cs.AI, cs.RO). The authors also propose new evaluation challenges, which involve system-level control and optimization (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), and computer vision (cs.CV).
